definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to a human family .
examples: Mark had to leave work due to familial obligations.

definitions.definition: Pertaining to a taxon at the rank of family .
examples: Having milky latex is a familial characteristic of Apocynaceae .

definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to any grouping of things referred to as a family .
examples: " Grandfather ", "mother", and "brother" are some English familial terms.

main_definition: Of or pertaining to a human family .
secondary_definitions: ( taxonomy ) Pertaining to a taxon at the rank of family .
Of or pertaining to any grouping of things referred to as a family .
